{{Infobox person|name=Sharon Stone|image=Sharon Stone by Gage Skidmore 3.jpg|caption=Stone ee 2017|birth_name=Sharon Vonne Stone|birth_date={{Birth date and age|1958|3|10}}|birth_place=[[Meadville, Pennsylvania]]|occupation=Atariisho|years_active=1980–hada|works=|spouse={{ubl|{{marriage|Michael Greenburg|1984|1990|end=f}}|{{marriage|[[Phil Bronstein]]|1998|2004|end=f}}}}|children=3|awards=}}'''Sharon Vonne Stone''' (dhashay Maarso 10, 1958) waa atariisho Mareykan ah, soo saare, iyo moodeel hore. Waxaa caan ku ah ku doorkeda sida [[Femme fatale|femme fatales]] iyo haweenka sirta ah ee filimada iyo telefishanka, waxay heshay abaalmarinno kala duwan, oo ay ku jiraan [[Abaalmarinta Emmy]] iyo [[Abaalmarinta Golden Globe]], marka lagu daro magacaabista [[Abaalmarinta Akadeemiyada]] iyo [[Abaalmarinta Jilayaasha Shaashada]].

Stone waxay bilaabay jilista 1980-kii, iyada kacay aqoonsi caalami ah markii ay u jilaysay [[Catherine Tramell]] ee ''[[Basic Instinct]]'' (1992), taas oo ay ku mutaystay abaal-marinteedii ugu horreysay ee [[Abaalmarinta Golden Globe ee Atariisho ugu Fiican Filim — Drama|Abaalmarinta Golden Globe ee Atariisho ugu Fiican Filim - Drama]]. Waxay heshay amaan dheeraad ah oo muhiim ah waxqabadkeeda ee filimka ''[[Casino]]'' (1995), iyada oo heshay Abaalmarinta Golden Globe iyo magacaabista [[Abaalmarinta Akadeemiyada ee Atariisho ugu Fiican]]. Stone ayaa markaas jishay filimkeedii labaad ee kacsiga, ''[[Sliver]]'' (1993).

